  <body>
    <p>This is the internal technical documentation for the Sámi
    pedagogical project.</p>

    <note> This documentation we have written mainly for
    <em>ourselves</em>, i.e. the project members, in order to keep track of things. 
    Other readers may read on, of course, but be prepared to see 
    short-worded explanations and loose or obsolete thougts here and there.</note>
    <p>Our external documentation, for teachers
    and users  is found at <a
    href="http://giellatekno.uit.no/oahpa">giellatekno.uit.no/oahpa/</a>. For
    the time being it is in Sámi and (partly) in Norwegian only (the VISL games are
    documented in English at the <a
    href="http://visl.sdu.dk/">visl.sdu.dk</a> site). User 
    documentation in other languages (English, Finnish) is forthcoming, but later.</p>

